60|$|I was {{carrying}} a beautiful alcoholic conflagration around with me. The thing fed on its own heat and flamed the fiercer. There was no time, in all my waking time, that I didn't <b>want</b> <b>a</b> <b>drink.</b> I began to anticipate the completion of my daily thousand words by taking a drink when only five hundred words were written. It was not long until I prefaced {{the beginning of the}} thousand words with a drink.|$|E
